# zk-Rollup Blueprint

zk-Rollups are one of the most important breakthroughs in blockchain scalability.  
They combine off-chain computation with on-chain verification using zero-knowledge proofs â€” allowing thousands of transactions to be processed securely and privately.

This repository aims to be a clear and concise blueprint to understand:
- The technology behind zk-Rollups  
- The main Layer 2 ecosystems using zk proofs  
- The trade-offs between scalability, security, and decentralization  
- The social and philosophical implications of a world where â€œproof replaces trustâ€  

